name: Import Cost Sheet
query:
SELECT
`tabImport Cost Sheet`.name as "ID:200",
  `tabImport Cost Sheet`.purchase_order_no as "Purchase Order No:200",
  `tabImport Cost Sheet`.purchase_invoice as "Purchase Invoice:Link/Purchase Invoice:200",
   `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.parameters as "Parameters:Link/Item:200",
   `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.sea_fright_etb as "Sea Fright:200",
   `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.inland_fright_etb as "Inland Fright:200",
  `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.insurance_etb as "Insurance:200",
   `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.import_customs_duty_etb as "Import Customs Duty:200",
   `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.other_etb as "Other:200",
  `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.bank_charge_etb as "Bank charge:200",
   `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.storage_etb as "Storage:200",
   `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.port_handling_charge_etb as "Port handling charge:200",
  `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.transit_and_clearing_etb as "Transit and clearing:200",
   `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.loading_and_unloading_etb as "Loading and unloading:200",
   `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.inland_transport_etb as "Inland transport:200",
    `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.miscellaneous_etb as "Miscellaneous:200",
    `tabImport Cost Sheet`.net_total as "Total:400"
FROM
  `tabImport Cost Sheet`
  join
  `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`
  on
  `tabImport Cost Sheet`.name = `tabImport Cost Sheet Details`.parent
